Project CODERUNNER - Version 2.2 - 23 Mar 2026

This is a CGI FORM for running Code. 

There is mainly a FORM. And some radio buttons to select the programming 
language. And then a RUN button.

That is all.

The output is displayed below the HTML. There are several options. There is a 
way to pass arguments (to the code, not the binaries).

Requirements

Any wanted language to be used is expected to be be installed and available as 
a single binary, and configured in in the source - BIN.SH. And, of course, a 
LOCALHOST server able to run .cgi code in a directory.

Installation

Just place all the code somewhere nice within your LOCALHOST server's space.

Example

    http://localhost/coderun/coderun.cgi
